race.comment: JAKE PERALTA (6) last start finished 4th over 300m at this track beaten 6 lengths (17.91) behind Scarlet's Rocket in a Mix 2/3 on January 10. Looks a key player on best form. WE WILL SEE (2) finished second (17.74) two back at this track but out of the placings last time when 6th there. A big run wouldn't surprise. CLOCK THE ZIPPER (1) turned in a plain effort last time when sixth at Casino over 300m behind Slimy Trout (17.60) in a Mix 3/4. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to his credit. Should be about the money. ANOTHER ONE (3) has been in the money at her last two runs, most recently when second (17.99) in a Grade 5 over 300m at this track.
